jar = CookieJar()
cookie = Cookie(b'Name', b'Value', domain=cookie_domain)
with pytest.raises(InvalidCookieDomain):
    jar.add(request_url, cookie)
pytest.mark.parametrize('request_url,cookie_domain', [[URL(
    b'https://bezkitu.org'), b'example.com'], [URL(
    b'https://foo.bezkitu.org'), b'baz.foo.bezkitu.org'], [URL(
    b'https://foo.bezkitu.org'), b'foo.org']])
